          "\"Thy heart hath Brynhild",
          "whetted to hate,",
          "Evil to work",
          "and harm to win,",
          "She grudges the honor",
          "that Guthrun has,",
          "And that joy of herself",
          "thou still dost have.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "\"They cooked a wolf,",
