          "They gave to Gotthorm",
          "the greedy one's flesh,",
          "Before the men,",
          "to murder minded,",
          "Laid their hands",
          "on the hero bold.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Slain was Sigurth",
          "south of the Rhine;",
          "From a limb a raven",
          "called full loud:",
          "Your blood shall redden",
          "Atli's blade,",
          "And your oaths shall bind",
