          "Sigurth's killer,",
          "Vengeance shall come",
          "for his cruel heart.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "12",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "12.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Early came evening,",
          "and ale was drunk,",
          "And among them long",
          "and loud they talked.;",
          "They slumbered all",
          "when their beds they sought,",
          "But Gunnar alone",
          "was long awake.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "13",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "13.",
        "lines": [
          "\"His feet were tossing,",
          "he talked to himself,",
          "And the slayer of hosts",
          "began to heed",
          "What the twain from the tree",
