          "The warrior's daughter,",
          "ere dawn of day:",
          "Love me or hate me,",
          "the harm is done,",
          "And my grief cries out,",
          "or else I die.\""
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "15.",
        "lines": [
          "\"Silent were all",
